<li>I'm so incredibly sorry to hear about the loss of your friend.</li>
<li>My heart goes out to you during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and sending my deepest condolences.</li>
<li>I'll always remember [friend's name]'s kind spirit.</li>
<li>Your friend will be deeply missed.  May God grant you peace.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and comfort as you grieve.</li>
<li>I'm here for you, whatever you need.</li>
<li>I'm deeply saddened by the news of your loss.</li>
<li>May God's loving arms surround you during this time.</li>
<li>Your friend's memory will live on in our hearts.</li>
<li>May fond memories bring you solace.</li>
<li>Praying for peace and comfort for you.</li>
<li>My thoughts are with you in your sorrow.</li>
<li>May God's grace carry you through your grief.</li>
