<p>May God's grace and comfort surround you now and in the days to come.  Grief is a journey, and you are not alone on this path.  Though sadness may linger, may faith provide solace, and memories bring a gentle warmth to your heart.  May peace find you, and may the love of those around you strengthen you through this time of sorrow.</p>
    
  
